00:00:04.940 --> 00:00:08.860
 250 g of almonds and 400 g of peanuts are drawn in the robot. 

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:12.100
 You can use the desired nuts. 

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:16.040
 Half a teaspoon of cinnamon 

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:20.380
 1 tea cup is mixed with honey. 

00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:36.560
 The mixture prepared on the greased paper tray is poured and spread evenly to each corner of the tray. 

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.440
 It is pressed with 1 cup on it. 

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:53.280
 200 g of bitter chocolate is melted over and over. 

00:01:08.020 --> 00:01:15.300
 After waiting for the chocolate to freeze, the tray is inverted and the chocolate surface is placed underneath. 

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:25.320
 200 g of milk chocolate is poured over, and then melted into 100 g white chocolate strips. 

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:41.220
 With the help of the knife, lines are formed up and down. 

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:03.420
 The chocolates on the top layer are cut and then sliced. 

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:06.960
 If it freezes too much, it can be difficult to cut. 

00:02:07.140 --> 00:02:08.680
 Enjoy your meal. 

